    <div class=" col-3">
      <div class="col-auto">
        <p class="mb-0 me-2">Currency:</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-3">
        <select id="inputCurrency" class="form-select">
          <option selected value="KES">KES</option>
          <option value="$">$</option>
          <option value="TZS">TZS</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3>Pricing based on your business size</h3>
  <p id="text-e">create your eCommerce website. Then choose the best plan for your idea and budget – pricing only goes up when your business grows. No lock-in, no hidden fees, no credit card needed.</p>
  <div class="justify-content-center mt-5">
    <p><strong>Biling Period</strong></p>
    <span class="mr-3 bv">Monthly</span>
    <label class="switch">
      <input type="checkbox" id="billing-switch" checked>
      <span class="slider round"></span>
  </label>
  <span class="ml-3 bv">Semi-annually</span>
  </div>
  <div class="row pricing-column">
