  <div class="pricing-extra-content">
    <ol>
      <h5><strong>About Namarunu-store pricing</strong></h5>
      <li>Namarunu doesn't take any fee from transactions. However, payment gateway fees from Mpesa or flutterwave may apply and are usually around 3%–4%</li>
      <li>Hosting, maintenance, backups, and updates are included in your plan. When new features are released, your eCommerce website is automatically updated.</li>
      <li>Prices do not include VAT.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
